skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: funny inspirational quotes
des:
Start your day with an inspirational list of quotes by famous people. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
